    "description": "<p>For the duration, you deal +1 Lightning damage on Martial Attacks.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Damage: (2 MP, Repeatable)</strong> Your Attacks affected by this Spell deal +1 Lightning damage.</p><p><strong>Effortless: (1 MP)</strong> You no longer need to Sustain the Spell.</p><p><strong>Chain Lightning: (X MP)</strong> Once per Round, when you make an Attack affected by this Spell, you can choose 1 additional target within 3 Spaces of the original target using the same Martial Attack for the additional target. <strong>Hit:</strong> The Target takes X Lightning damage.</p><p><strong>Static Strike: (X MP)</strong> Once per round, 1 target of an Attack affected by this Spell makes a Physical Save against your Save DC. <strong>Save Failure:</strong> For the next round, the first time the target willingly moves or takes a Reaction it takes X Lightning damage.</p>",
